02:12:15.352 --> 02:12:18.810
- Birdsong! Son, you OK?
- Crazy black bastard!

02:12:18.856 --> 02:12:20.653
- Come here.
- Help me get him.

02:12:20.691 --> 02:12:22.283
[in Italian] Get back. Get back.

02:12:22.326 --> 02:12:23.850
Let me take him.

02:12:25.062 --> 02:12:28.259
- I'll see you again, Stamps.
- I hope so.

