02:15:48.032 --> 02:15:51.695
I knew it. I knew it...

02:15:55.773 --> 02:15:59.573
Train, I'm gonna take this kid,
and I'm gonna come back for you.

02:15:59.610 --> 02:16:01.339
I'm gonna come right back for you.

02:16:01.378 --> 02:16:03.243
