02:23:16.213 --> 02:23:17.703
Guys, we need a hand.

02:23:22.719 --> 02:23:25.153
Stand by. Lift!

02:23:37.400 --> 02:23:40.233
[man] Easy, y'all. Real easy.

02:23:40.270 --> 02:23:44.434
It's gonna be OK, Hector. You're going
