02:23:52.849 --> 02:23:55.113
[man 2] Reconnaissance photos
were accurate.

02:23:55.152 --> 02:23:58.212
General Almond wouldn't listen.
Go get those dog tags.

02:23:58.255 --> 02:23:59.552
[man 3] Yes, sir.

02:23:59.589 --> 02:24:01.784
[man 2] I need a full report,
on the double.

02:24:03.326 --> 02:24:05.886
- [man 3] "Stamps, Aubrey."
- [man 4] Got it.

02:24:07.898 --> 02:24:10.594
- [man 3] "Cummings, Bishop."
- [man 4] Check.

02:24:13.670 --> 02:24:16.138
- [man 3] "Train, Samuel."
- [man 4] Got it.

02:24:23.547 --> 02:24:26.641
Well done, corporal.
You earned yourself a Purple Heart.

02:24:26.683 --> 02:24:29.117
- Get this man to the aid station.
- Yes, sir!

02:24:29.152 --> 02:24:30.676
Detail.

02:24:38.461 --> 02:24:41.396
[Tim] Come on, Mr. Negron.
You're clean as a board of health.

02:24:41.431 --> 02:24:46.960
